model.ad_lite.results_dq_recency.name: results_dq_recency
model.ad_lite.results_dq_recency.compiled_code:
/*to do: just like  dbt_valid_from  is the dbt  snapshot date, the default cdc date is  dbt_updated_at, however, it is some sort of dwh_insert_datetime    */
/*to do: make completeness a macro */
/*to do: add table name ! to final query  */ 
/*to do: add loop based on values returned in a string from information_schema.tables  */

SELECT DV.dbt_valid_from, 

		/* Make the datawarehouse controlled columns additive, by including them once. */
		CASE WHEN FIRST_VALUE(SV.count_date) OVER (ORDER BY SV.days_diff) = SV.count_date
				THEN DV.D_Count_dwhInsertDatetime
				ELSE NULL END AS D_Count_dwhInsertDatetime,
				
		CASE WHEN FIRST_VALUE(SV.count_date) OVER (ORDER BY SV.days_diff) = SV.count_date
				THEN DV.First_dwhInsertDatetime
				ELSE NULL END AS First_dwhInsertDatetime,
				
		CASE WHEN FIRST_VALUE(SV.count_date) OVER (ORDER BY SV.days_diff) = SV.count_date
				THEN DV.Last_dwhInsertDatetime
				ELSE NULL END AS Last_dwhInsertDatetime,

		CASE WHEN FIRST_VALUE(SV.count_date) OVER (ORDER BY SV.days_diff) = SV.count_date
				THEN DV.count_distinct_surrogate_key
				ELSE NULL END AS count_distinct_surrogate_key,
				
		CASE WHEN FIRST_VALUE(SV.count_date) OVER (ORDER BY SV.days_diff) = SV.count_date
				THEN DV.sum_transactions
				ELSE NULL END AS sum_transactions,

		SV.* except(dbt_valid_from)
FROM (

SELECT 	dbt_valid_from,
		COUNT(DISTINCT(DATE_TRUNC(CDCTransDateTime, DAY))) 		AS D_Count_dwhInsertDatetime,	
		/* In data quality the minimum is used on dbt / dwh datetime is used to establish boundary entry	*/
		MIN(CDCTransDateTime)									AS First_dwhInsertDatetime,	
		/* In data quality the maximum is used on dbt / dwh datetime is used to establish boundary exit		*/
		MAX(CDCTransDateTime)									AS Last_dwhInsertDatetime,			
		/********************************/
		COUNT(DISTINCT(stg_composite_key))							AS count_distinct_surrogate_key,
		SUM(1)																AS sum_transactions		
 FROM `sample-project`.`adventureworks_stg_ds`.`stg_Purchasing_PurchaseOrderDetail`
 WHERE '2011-06-01' =  dbt_valid_from
 GROUP BY dbt_valid_from
) DV
LEFT JOIN (

	SELECT tiled.*
		, date_diff(DATE '2011-06-01', count_date, day ) AS days_diff 
        FROM
			(SELECT A.*, NTILE(100) OVER (ORDER BY count_value) AS ordered_count
			 FROM 
				(
				SELECT   dbt_valid_from	, CAST(ModifiedDate  AS DATE) AS count_date, 
					COUNT(1) AS count_value
				FROM `sample-project`.`adventureworks_stg_ds`.`stg_Purchasing_PurchaseOrderDetail`
				WHERE    dbt_valid_from =  '2011-06-01'
						GROUP BY    dbt_valid_from	, CAST(ModifiedDate  AS DATE)
				) A
			) tiled
QUALIFY ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY ordered_count ORDER BY count_value DESC, count_date 
			 ASC ) = 1


) SV 
	ON DV.dbt_valid_from = SV.dbt_valid_from
ORDER BY ordered_count DESC, count_date

model.ad_lite.results_dq_schema_drift.name: results_dq_schema_drift
model.ad_lite.results_dq_schema_drift.compiled_code:
with a as (

    
select * except(process_date, dbt_scd_id, dbt_updated_at,dbt_valid_from,dbt_valid_to)
 FROM `sample-project`.`data_quality`.`dq_schema_drift`
 qualify row_number() over (partition by table_schema, table_name, column_name order by process_date desc) = 2


),

b as (

    
select * except(process_date, dbt_scd_id, dbt_updated_at,dbt_valid_from,dbt_valid_to)
 FROM `sample-project`.`data_quality`.`dq_schema_drift`
 qualify row_number() over (partition by table_schema, table_name, column_name order by process_date desc) = 1


),


a_except_b as (

    select * from a
    

    except distinct


    select * from b

),

b_except_a as (

    select * from b
    

    except distinct


    select * from a

),

all_records as (

    select
        true as in_a,
        false as in_b,
		*
    from a_except_b

    union all

    select
        false as in_a,
        true as in_b,
		*
    from b_except_a

),


final as (
    
    select * from all_records
    where not (in_a and in_b)
    order by drift_hkey,  in_a desc, in_b desc

)

select * from final

SELECT FARM_FINGERPRINT(CONCAT(BOM.stg_BillOfMaterials_key,REPLACE('{{ var('dbt_BusinessDate') }}','-',''))) AS baw_BillOfMaterials_key, BOM.stg_BillOfMaterials_key,  
	BOM.ComponentID, IFNULL(BOM.ProductAssemblyID,0) AS ProductAssemblyID, /*Natural Key */
	/*Product*/
	Pt.ProductNumber, Pt.ProductName, /*Product Unique Keys*/
	Pt.ProductModelID, Pt.ProductModelName,Pt.CatalogDescription,Pt.Instructions,
	Pt.ProductSubcategoryName,
	Pt.ProductCategoryName,
	/*Bill Of Model Materials*/
	BOM.StartDate AS StartDate,BOM.EndDate AS EndDate,BOM.UnitMeasureCode AS UnitMeasureCode, UM2.Name AS UnitMeasureName,
	BOM.BOMLevel, BOM.PerAssemblyQty,
	'{{ var('dbt_BusinessDate') }}' AS ModifiedDate
FROM  {{ ref('stg_Build_BillOfMaterials') }} AS BOM
JOIN  {{ ref('dim2_Common_Product') }} AS Pt 
	ON BOM.stg_Component_key =Pt.stg_Product_key AND '{{ var('dbt_BusinessDate') }}' BETWEEN  Pt.dbt_valid_from AND IFNULL(Pt.dbt_valid_to,'2099-06-06')

LEFT JOIN {{ ref('stg_Person_PhoneNumberType') }} AS PNT3

SELECT FARM_FINGERPRINT(CONCAT(C.stg_Customer_key,REPLACE('{{ var('dbt_BusinessDate') }}','-',''))) AS baw_Customer_key, C.stg_Customer_key,
	C.stg_Person_key AS stg_Customer_BusinessEntity_key,C.stg_Store_key AS stg_Store_key,
	C.stg_Territory_key AS Customer_Territory_key,
	SPn.stg_BusinessEntity_key AS SalesPerson_BusinessEntity_key, SPn.dbt_valid_from AS SalesPerson_dbt_valid_from,
	SPn.stg_Territory_key AS SalesPerson_Territory_key,
	/*ACCOUNT DATA*/
	C.AccountNumber AS CustomerAccountNumber,
	Pn1.Title AS CustTitle,Pn1.AdditionalContactInfo AS CustAdditionalContactInfo,Pn1.Demographics AS CustDemographicsXML,Pn1.PersonType AS CustPersonType ,Pn1.NameStyle AS CustNameStyle,
	Pn1.FirstName AS CustFirstName, Pn1.MiddleName AS CustMIddleName,Pn1.LastName AS CustLastName,Pn1.Suffix AS CustSuffix,
	ST1.Name AS CustSalesTerritory,ST1.CountryRegionCode AS CustCountryRegionCode, CRn1.Name AS CustCountryRegionName,
	FIRST_VALUE(EA.EmailAddress) OVER (PARTITION BY EA.stg_BusinessEntity_key ORDER BY EA.ModifiedDate DESC, EA.stg_composite_key DESC) AS EmailAddress, 
	FIRST_VALUE(CASE WHEN PNT1.Name IS NULL THEN '' ELSE PPe1.PhoneNumber END) OVER (PARTITION BY PPe1.stg_BusinessEntity_key ORDER BY PPe1.ModifiedDate DESC, PPe1.PhoneNumber DESC) AS WorkPhone,
	FIRST_VALUE(CASE WHEN PNT2.Name IS NULL THEN '' ELSE PPe2.PhoneNumber END) OVER (PARTITION BY PPe2.stg_BusinessEntity_key ORDER BY PPe2.ModifiedDate DESC, PPe2.PhoneNumber DESC) AS HomePhone,
	FIRST_VALUE(CASE WHEN PNT3.Name IS NULL THEN '' ELSE PPe3.PhoneNumber END) OVER (PARTITION BY PPe3.stg_BusinessEntity_key ORDER BY PPe3.ModifiedDate DESC, PPe3.PhoneNumber DESC) AS MobilePhone,	
	/*STORE DATA*/
	Se.Demographics AS StoreDemographicsXML,Se.Name AS StoreName,
	/*PAYMENT DATA*/
	CC.CardType,CC.CardNumber,CONCAT(COALESCE(CAST(CC.ExpMonth as string),'00'),'-',COALESCE(CAST(CC.ExpYear as string),'00')) AS CardExpDate,
	/*SALESPERSON DATA*/
	Pn.Title AS SalespersonTitle,Pn.PersonType  AS SalespersonPersonType ,
	Pn.FirstName AS SalespersonFirstName, Pn.MiddleName AS SalespersonMiddleName,Pn.LastName AS SalespersonLastName,Pn.Suffix AS SalespersonSuffix, 
	ST.Name AS SalespersonSalesTerritory,ST.CountryRegionCode AS SalespersonCountryRegionCode, CRn.Name AS SalespersonCountryRegionName,
	'{{ var('dbt_BusinessDate') }}' AS ModifiedDate
FROM {{ ref('stg_Sales_Customer') }} AS C
JOIN {{ source('Sales-stg', 'dl_dim2_Sales_Customer') }} AS ddl
	ON C.stg_Customer_key = ddl.stg_Customer_key
	AND C.dbt_valid_from = ddl.dbt_valid_from

snapshot.ad_lite.fact_Build_WorkOrderRou.name: fact_Build_WorkOrderRouting
snapshot.ad_lite.fact_Build_WorkOrderRou.raw_code:
{{
	config(
		target_database=var('gcp_Project'),
		target_schema=var('gcp_DataSet_baw'),
		strategy='check',		
		unique_key='baw_WorkOrder_key',
		cluster_by = 'baw_Product_key',	
		updated_at='ModifiedDate',		
		check_cols=['ScheduledStartDate','ScheduledEndDate','ActualStartDate','ActualEndDate','ActualResourceHrs'
		,'PlannedCost','ActualCost','WorkOrderStartDate','WorkOrderEndDate','WorkOrderDueDate','WorkOrderOrderQty','WorkOrderStockedQty','WorkOrderScrappedQty',
		'DailyQty'
		],
	)
}}

WITH DL AS
	(SELECT WOR.stg_composite_key,  WOR.dbt_valid_from
	FROM  {{ ref('stg_Build_WorkOrderRouting') }} AS WOR
	WHERE '{{var('dbt_Layer')}}' = 'baw' AND WOR.dbt_valid_from ='{{var('dbt_BusinessDate')}}'  
	--
	UNION ALL
    --
	SELECT 	WOR.stg_composite_key,  WOR.dbt_valid_from
	FROM  {{ ref('stg_Build_WorkOrderRouting') }} AS WOR
	JOIN  {{ ref('stg_Build_WorkOrder') }} AS WO 
	ON WOR.stg_WorkOrder_key=WO.stg_WorkOrder_key
	WHERE '{{ var('dbt_BusinessDate') }}' BETWEEN  WOR.dbt_valid_from AND IFNULL(WOR.dbt_valid_to,'2099-06-06') 
	AND '{{var('dbt_Layer')}}' = 'baw' AND WO.dbt_valid_from ='{{var('dbt_BusinessDate')}}'  
	--
	UNION ALL
    --
	SELECT 	WOR.stg_composite_key,  WOR.dbt_valid_from
	FROM  {{ ref('stg_Build_WorkOrderRouting') }} AS WOR
	JOIN  {{ ref('dim2_Common_Product') }} AS Pt 
	ON WOR.stg_Product_key=Pt.stg_Product_key  
	WHERE '{{ var('dbt_BusinessDate') }}' BETWEEN  WOR.dbt_valid_from AND IFNULL(WOR.dbt_valid_to,'2099-06-06') 
	AND '{{var('dbt_Layer')}}' = 'baw' AND Pt.dbt_valid_from ='{{var('dbt_BusinessDate')}}'  
	--
	UNION ALL
    --
	SELECT 	WOR.stg_composite_key,  WOR.dbt_valid_from
	FROM  {{ ref('stg_Build_WorkOrderRouting') }} AS WOR
	JOIN  {{ ref('dim2_Build_ProductInventory') }} AS Pin
	ON WOR.stg_Product_key=Pin.stg_Product_key  
	WHERE '{{ var('dbt_BusinessDate') }}' BETWEEN  WOR.dbt_valid_from AND IFNULL(WOR.dbt_valid_to,'2099-06-06') 
	AND '{{var('dbt_Layer')}}' = 'baw' AND Pin.dbt_valid_from ='{{var('dbt_BusinessDate')}}'  ) 
, DDL AS 
	(SELECT stg_composite_key, max(dbt_valid_from) as dbt_valid_from
	FROM DL
	GROUP BY stg_composite_key)

SELECT FARM_FINGERPRINT(CONCAT(WOR.stg_composite_key, REPLACE('{{ var('dbt_BusinessDate') }}','-',''))) as baw_WorkOrder_key,
	WOR.stg_composite_key,
	WOR.stg_WorkOrder_key,
	WOR.stg_Product_key,
	WOR.OperationSequence,
	WOR.stg_Location_key,  
	Pin.baw_ProductInventory_key,
	IFNULL(SR1.baw_ScrapReason_key,0) AS baw_ScrapReason_key,
	Pt.baw_Product_key,
	/*WorkOrderRouting Details*/
	WOR.ScheduledStartDate,WOR.ScheduledEndDate,
	WOR.ActualStartDate,WOR.ActualEndDate,WOR.ActualResourceHrs,
	WOR.PlannedCost,WOR.ActualCost,
	/*WorkOrder Details*/
	WO.StartDate AS WorkOrderStartDate,WO.EndDate AS WorkOrderEndDate,WO.DueDate AS WorkOrderDueDate,
	WO.OrderQty AS WorkOrderOrderQty, WO.StockedQty AS WorkOrderStockedQty, WO.ScrappedQty AS WorkOrderScrappedQty,
	/*Product Inventory facts*/
	FIRST_VALUE(Pin1.Quantity) OVER(PARTITION BY WOR.stg_Product_key, WOR.stg_Location_key ORDER BY WOR.stg_WorkOrder_key, WOR.OperationSequence) as DailyQty,
	'{{ var('dbt_BusinessDate') }}' AS ModifiedDate
FROM  {{ ref('stg_Build_WorkOrderRouting') }} AS WOR
JOIN DDL 
	ON WOR.stg_composite_key = DDL.stg_composite_key
	AND WOR.dbt_valid_from = DDL.dbt_valid_from
JOIN  {{ ref('stg_Build_WorkOrder') }} AS WO 
	ON WOR.stg_WorkOrder_key=WO.stg_WorkOrder_key
	AND '{{ var('dbt_BusinessDate') }}' BETWEEN  WO.dbt_valid_from AND IFNULL(WO.dbt_valid_to,'2099-06-06')
JOIN  {{ ref('dim2_Common_Product') }} AS Pt 
	ON WOR.stg_Product_key=Pt.stg_Product_key  
	AND '{{ var('dbt_BusinessDate') }}' BETWEEN  Pt.dbt_valid_from AND IFNULL(Pt.dbt_valid_to,'2099-06-06')

snapshot.ad_lite.fact_Build_WorkOrderRou.compiled_code:
WITH DL AS
	(SELECT WOR.stg_composite_key,  WOR.dbt_valid_from
	FROM  `sample-project`.`adventureworks_stg_ds`.`stg_Build_WorkOrderRouting` AS WOR
	WHERE 'raw' = 'baw' AND WOR.dbt_valid_from ='2011-06-01'  
	--
	UNION ALL
    --
	SELECT 	WOR.stg_composite_key,  WOR.dbt_valid_from
	FROM  `sample-project`.`adventureworks_stg_ds`.`stg_Build_WorkOrderRouting` AS WOR
	JOIN  `sample-project`.`adventureworks_stg_ds`.`stg_Build_WorkOrder` AS WO 
	ON WOR.stg_WorkOrder_key=WO.stg_WorkOrder_key
	WHERE '2011-06-01' BETWEEN  WOR.dbt_valid_from AND IFNULL(WOR.dbt_valid_to,'2099-06-06') 
	AND 'raw' = 'baw' AND WO.dbt_valid_from ='2011-06-01'  
	--
	UNION ALL
    --
	SELECT 	WOR.stg_composite_key,  WOR.dbt_valid_from
	FROM  `sample-project`.`adventureworks_stg_ds`.`stg_Build_WorkOrderRouting` AS WOR
	JOIN  `sample-project`.`adventureworks_baw_ds`.`dim2_Common_Product` AS Pt 
	ON WOR.stg_Product_key=Pt.stg_Product_key  
	WHERE '2011-06-01' BETWEEN  WOR.dbt_valid_from AND IFNULL(WOR.dbt_valid_to,'2099-06-06') 
	AND 'raw' = 'baw' AND Pt.dbt_valid_from ='2011-06-01'  
	--
	UNION ALL
    --
	SELECT 	WOR.stg_composite_key,  WOR.dbt_valid_from
	FROM  `sample-project`.`adventureworks_stg_ds`.`stg_Build_WorkOrderRouting` AS WOR
	JOIN  `sample-project`.`adventureworks_baw_ds`.`dim2_Build_ProductInventory` AS Pin
	ON WOR.stg_Product_key=Pin.stg_Product_key  
	WHERE '2011-06-01' BETWEEN  WOR.dbt_valid_from AND IFNULL(WOR.dbt_valid_to,'2099-06-06') 
	AND 'raw' = 'baw' AND Pin.dbt_valid_from ='2011-06-01'  ) 
, DDL AS 
	(SELECT stg_composite_key, max(dbt_valid_from) as dbt_valid_from
	FROM DL
	GROUP BY stg_composite_key)

SELECT FARM_FINGERPRINT(CONCAT(WOR.stg_composite_key, REPLACE('2011-06-01','-',''))) as baw_WorkOrder_key,
	WOR.stg_composite_key,
	WOR.stg_WorkOrder_key,
	WOR.stg_Product_key,
	WOR.OperationSequence,
	WOR.stg_Location_key,  
	Pin.baw_ProductInventory_key,
	IFNULL(SR1.baw_ScrapReason_key,0) AS baw_ScrapReason_key,
	Pt.baw_Product_key,
	/*WorkOrderRouting Details*/
	WOR.ScheduledStartDate,WOR.ScheduledEndDate,
	WOR.ActualStartDate,WOR.ActualEndDate,WOR.ActualResourceHrs,
	WOR.PlannedCost,WOR.ActualCost,
	/*WorkOrder Details*/
	WO.StartDate AS WorkOrderStartDate,WO.EndDate AS WorkOrderEndDate,WO.DueDate AS WorkOrderDueDate,
	WO.OrderQty AS WorkOrderOrderQty, WO.StockedQty AS WorkOrderStockedQty, WO.ScrappedQty AS WorkOrderScrappedQty,
	/*Product Inventory facts*/
	FIRST_VALUE(Pin1.Quantity) OVER(PARTITION BY WOR.stg_Product_key, WOR.stg_Location_key ORDER BY WOR.stg_WorkOrder_key, WOR.OperationSequence) as DailyQty,
	'2011-06-01' AS ModifiedDate
FROM  `sample-project`.`adventureworks_stg_ds`.`stg_Build_WorkOrderRouting` AS WOR
JOIN DDL 
	ON WOR.stg_composite_key = DDL.stg_composite_key
	AND WOR.dbt_valid_from = DDL.dbt_valid_from
JOIN  `sample-project`.`adventureworks_stg_ds`.`stg_Build_WorkOrder` AS WO 
	ON WOR.stg_WorkOrder_key=WO.stg_WorkOrder_key
	AND '2011-06-01' BETWEEN  WO.dbt_valid_from AND IFNULL(WO.dbt_valid_to,'2099-06-06')
JOIN  `sample-project`.`adventureworks_baw_ds`.`dim2_Common_Product` AS Pt 
	ON WOR.stg_Product_key=Pt.stg_Product_key  
	AND '2011-06-01' BETWEEN  Pt.dbt_valid_from AND IFNULL(Pt.dbt_valid_to,'2099-06-06')
JOIN  `sample-project`.`adventureworks_baw_ds`.`dim2_Build_ProductInventory` AS Pin
	ON WOR.stg_Product_key=Pin.stg_Product_key  
	AND WOR.stg_Location_key=Pin.stg_Location_key  
	AND '2011-06-01' BETWEEN  Pin.dbt_valid_from AND IFNULL(Pin.dbt_valid_to,'2099-06-06')
JOIN  `sample-project`.`adventureworks_stg_ds`.`stg_Build_ProductInventory` AS Pin1
	ON WOR.stg_Product_key=Pin1.stg_Product_key  
	AND WOR.stg_Location_key=Pin1.stg_Location_key  
	AND '2011-06-01' BETWEEN  Pin1.dbt_valid_from AND IFNULL(Pin1.dbt_valid_to,'2099-06-06')	
	
LEFT JOIN  `sample-project`.`adventureworks_baw_ds`.`dim_Build_ScrapReason` AS SR1 
	ON WO.stg_ScrapReason_key=SR1.stg_ScrapReason_key	
WHERE '2011-06-01' BETWEEN WOR.dbt_valid_from AND IFNULL(WOR.dbt_valid_to,'2099-06-06') 
	AND 'raw' = 'baw'  AND WOR.dbt_valid_from ='2011-06-01'

{{
	config(
		target_database=var('gcp_Project'),
		target_schema=var('gcp_DataSet_baw'),
		strategy='check',		
		unique_key='baw_SalesOrderDetail_key',
		cluster_by = 'baw_Product_key',
		updated_at='ModifiedDate',		
		check_cols=['SalesReasonName_List','SalesOrder_Status','IsOnlineOrder','OrderComment','OrderRevisionNumber','OrderNumber','CustomerPONumber','CustomerAccountNumber','CreditCardApprovalCode','CarrierTrackingNumber','OrderPlacedDate','OrderDueDate','OrderShipDate','IsProduct','IsTax','IsFreight','LineOrder_Qty','LineUnit_Price','LineTotal_Price'
		],
		tags=['Sales','contains_pii'],
	)
}}
WITH DL AS
	(SELECT SOH.stg_SalesOrder_key
	FROM {{ ref('stg_Sales_SalesOrderHeader') }} AS SOH
	WHERE '{{var('dbt_Layer')}}' = 'baw'
		AND SOH.dbt_valid_from ='{{var('dbt_BusinessDate')}}'   
	---------
	UNION ALL
	---------
	SELECT SOD.stg_SalesOrder_key AS stg_SalesOrder_key
	FROM {{ ref('stg_Sales_SalesOrderDetail') }} AS SOD
	WHERE '{{var('dbt_Layer')}}' = 'baw'
		AND SOD.dbt_valid_from ='{{var('dbt_BusinessDate')}}' )		
	,DDL AS 
		(SELECT DISTINCT stg_SalesOrder_key FROM DL)		
	, SHR AS	
	(SELECT SOHSR.stg_SalesOrder_key, /*SOHSR.SalesReasonID, SR.SalesReasonName*/
		CONCAT("'",STRING_AGG(DISTINCT REPLACE(SR.SalesReasonName,' & ', ' AND '), "' & '") ,"'") AS SalesReasonName_List
	FROM {{ ref('stg_Sales_SalesOrderHeaderSalesReason') }} AS SOHSR
	JOIN {{ ref('stg_Sales_SalesReason') }} AS SR ON SOHSR.stg_SalesReason_key=SR.stg_SalesReason_key
		AND '{{var('dbt_BusinessDate')}}' BETWEEN  SOHSR.dbt_valid_from AND IFNULL(SOHSR.dbt_valid_to,'2099-06-06') 
	JOIN DDL 
		ON DDL.stg_SalesOrder_key = SOHSR.stg_SalesOrder_key
	GROUP BY SOHSR.stg_SalesOrder_key
	) 

SELECT FARM_FINGERPRINT(CONCAT(SOD.stg_composite_key, REPLACE('{{ var('dbt_BusinessDate') }}','-',''))) as baw_SalesOrderDetail_key, 
	SOD.stg_composite_key,
	Cu.baw_Customer_key,
    IFNULL(Sa.baw_SalesPerson_key,0) AS baw_SalesPerson_key,
    Pt.baw_Product_key,
	IFNULL(ST.baw_Territory_key,0) AS baw_Territory_key,
	AdB.baw_Address_key AS baw_BillToAddress_key,
	AdS.baw_Address_key AS baw_ShipToAddress_key,
	SR.baw_ShipMethod_key,
	IFNULL(CC.baw_CreditCard_key,0) AS baw_CreditCard_key,
	IFNULL(CR.baw_CurrencyRate_key,0) AS baw_CurrencyRate_key,	
	IFNULL(SO.baw_SpecialOffer_key,0) AS baw_SpecialOffer_key,
 	IFNULL(SHR.SalesReasonName_List,'') AS SalesReasonName_List,
	SOH.Status AS SalesOrder_Status, 
	SOH.OnlineOrderFlag AS IsOnlineOrder,
	SOH.Comment AS OrderComment,
	SOH.RevisionNumber AS OrderRevisionNumber,
	SOH.SalesOrderNumber AS OrderNumber,
	SOH.PurchaseOrderNumber AS CustomerPONumber,
	SOH.AccountNumber AS CustomerAccountNumber,
	SOH.CreditCardApprovalCode,
	SOD.CarrierTrackingNumber,
	SOH.OrderDate AS OrderPlacedDate,
	SOH.DueDate AS OrderDueDate,
	SOH.ShipDate AS OrderShipDate,
	1 as IsProduct,
	0 as IsTax,
	0 as IsFreight,
	SOD.OrderQty AS LineOrder_Qty,
	SOD.UnitPrice AS LineUnit_Price,
	SOD.LineTotal AS LineTotal_Price,
	'{{ var('dbt_BusinessDate') }}' AS ModifiedDate
FROM {{ ref('stg_Sales_SalesOrderDetail') }} AS SOD
JOIN {{ ref('stg_Sales_SalesOrderHeader') }} AS SOH 
	ON SOD.stg_SalesOrder_key=SOH.stg_SalesOrder_key
	AND '{{ var('dbt_BusinessDate') }}' BETWEEN  SOH.dbt_valid_from AND IFNULL(SOH.dbt_valid_to,'2099-06-06') 
/*SALES HEADER GRAIN*/
JOIN  {{ ref('dim2_Sales_Customer') }} AS Cu 
	ON SOH.stg_Customer_key=Cu.stg_Customer_key  
	AND '{{ var('dbt_BusinessDate') }}' BETWEEN  Cu.dbt_valid_from AND IFNULL(Cu.dbt_valid_to,'2099-06-06')
LEFT JOIN  {{ ref('dim2_Sales_SalesPerson') }} AS Sa 
	ON SOH.stg_BusinessEntity_key=Sa.stg_SalesPerson_key  
	AND '{{ var('dbt_BusinessDate') }}' BETWEEN  Sa.dbt_valid_from AND IFNULL(Sa.dbt_valid_to,'2099-06-06')
LEFT JOIN  {{ ref('dim2_Sales_SalesTerritory') }} AS ST 
	ON SOH.stg_Territory_key=ST.stg_Territory_key  
	AND '{{ var('dbt_BusinessDate') }}' BETWEEN  ST.dbt_valid_from AND IFNULL(ST.dbt_valid_to,'2099-06-06')
JOIN  {{ ref('dim2_Person_Address') }} AS AdB 
	ON SOH.stg_BillToAddress_key=AdB.stg_Address_key  
	AND '{{ var('dbt_BusinessDate') }}' BETWEEN  AdB.dbt_valid_from AND IFNULL(AdB.dbt_valid_to,'2099-06-06')
JOIN  {{ ref('dim2_Person_Address') }} AS AdS 
	ON SOH.stg_ShipToAddress_key=AdS.stg_Address_key  
	AND '{{ var('dbt_BusinessDate') }}' BETWEEN  AdS.dbt_valid_from AND IFNULL(AdS.dbt_valid_to,'2099-06-06')
LEFT JOIN  {{ ref('dim2_Sales_CreditCard') }} AS CC 
	ON SOH.stg_CreditCard_key=CC.stg_CreditCard_key 
	AND '{{ var('dbt_BusinessDate') }}' BETWEEN  CC.dbt_valid_from AND IFNULL(CC.dbt_valid_to,'2099-06-06')
LEFT JOIN  {{ ref('dim2_Sales_CurrencyRate') }} AS CR 
	ON SOH.stg_CurrencyRate_key=CR.stg_CurrencyRate_key 	
	AND '{{ var('dbt_BusinessDate') }}' BETWEEN  CR.dbt_valid_from AND IFNULL(CR.dbt_valid_to,'2099-06-06')
JOIN {{ ref('dim_Purchasing_ShipMethod') }} AS SR
	ON SOH.stg_ShipMethod_key=SR.stg_ShipMethod_key /*SCD TYPE 1*/
 LEFT JOIN SHR
	ON SOH.stg_SalesOrder_key=SHR.stg_SalesOrder_key 
/*SALES DETAIL GRAIN*/
JOIN {{ ref('dim2_Common_Product') }} AS Pt 
	ON SOD.stg_Product_key=Pt.stg_Product_key  
	AND '{{ var('dbt_BusinessDate') }}' BETWEEN  Pt.dbt_valid_from AND IFNULL(Pt.dbt_valid_to,'2099-06-06')
LEFT JOIN  {{ ref('dim2_Sales_SpecialOffer') }} AS SO
	ON SOD.stg_SpecialOffer_key=SO.stg_SpecialOffer_key  
	AND '{{ var('dbt_BusinessDate') }}' BETWEEN  SO.dbt_valid_from AND IFNULL(SO.dbt_valid_to,'2099-06-06')
JOIN DDL 
	ON DDL.stg_SalesOrder_key = SOH.stg_SalesOrder_key	
WHERE '{{ var('dbt_BusinessDate') }}' BETWEEN  SOD.dbt_valid_from AND IFNULL(SOD.dbt_valid_to,'2099-06-06') 	
---------
UNION ALL
---------
 SELECT FARM_FINGERPRINT(CONCAT('IsTax', SOH.stg_SalesOrder_key, REPLACE('{{ var('dbt_BusinessDate') }}','-',''))) as baw_SalesOrderDetail_key,

	AND '{{ var('dbt_BusinessDate') }}' BETWEEN  AdB.dbt_valid_from AND IFNULL(AdB.dbt_valid_to,'2099-06-06')
JOIN  {{ ref('dim2_Person_Address') }} AS AdS 
	ON SOH.stg_ShipToAddress_key=AdS.stg_Address_key  
	AND '{{ var('dbt_BusinessDate') }}' BETWEEN  AdS.dbt_valid_from AND IFNULL(AdS.dbt_valid_to,'2099-06-06')

LEFT JOIN  {{ ref('dim2_Sales_CurrencyRate') }} AS CR 
	ON SOH.stg_CurrencyRate_key=CR.stg_CurrencyRate_key 	
	AND '{{ var('dbt_BusinessDate') }}' BETWEEN  CR.dbt_valid_from AND IFNULL(CR.dbt_valid_to,'2099-06-06')
JOIN {{ ref('dim_Purchasing_ShipMethod') }} AS SR

snapshot.ad_lite.stg_Build_BillOfMateria.name: stg_Build_BillOfMaterials
snapshot.ad_lite.stg_Build_BillOfMateria.description: Contains a list of all the components used to manufacture bicycles and bicycle subassemblies.ProductAssemblyIDrepresents the parent (or primary) product andComponentIDrepresents child (or individual) parts that are used to build the parent assembly. For example, a wheel assembly contains components such as reflectors, rims, spokes, tires, and tire tubes.

BOMLevel.name: BOMLevel
BOMLevel.description: Indicates the depth the component is from its parent (ProductAssemblyID).

ComponentID.name: ComponentID
ComponentID.description: Component identification number. Foreign key toProduct.ProductID.

EndDate.name: EndDate
EndDate.description: Date the component stopped being used in the assembly item.

PerAssemblyQty.name: PerAssemblyQty
PerAssemblyQty.description: Quantity of the component needed to create the assembly.

ProductAssemblyID.name: ProductAssemblyID
ProductAssemblyID.description: Parent product identification number. Foreign key toProduct.ProductID.

StartDate.name: StartDate
StartDate.description: Date the component started being used in the assembly item.

UnitMeasureCode.name: UnitMeasureCode
UnitMeasureCode.description: Standard code identifying the unit of measure for the quantity.

ModifiedDate.name: ModifiedDate
ModifiedDate.description: Date and time the row was last updated.

	WHERE CDCTransDateTime >= CAST('2011-06-01' AS TIMESTAMP) AND CDCTransDateTime < CAST(DATE_ADD(DATE '2011-06-01', INTERVAL 1 DAY) AS TIMESTAMP)

{# This is the distinct driving list for the dim2_Purchasing_Vendor #}

{# dl_dim2_Purchasing_Vendor #}


WITH DL AS
	(
	SELECT E.stg_BusinessEntity_key, E.dbt_valid_from
	FROM {{ source('Purchasing-stg', 'stg_Purchasing_Vendor') }} AS E 
	WHERE '{{ var('dbt_BusinessDate') }}' BETWEEN  E.dbt_valid_from AND IFNULL(E.dbt_valid_to,'2099-06-06') 
	AND '{{var('dbt_Layer')}}' = 'stg' AND E.dbt_valid_from ='{{var('dbt_BusinessDate')}}' 
	--
	UNION ALL
    --
    SELECT Pn.stg_BusinessEntity_key, Pn.dbt_valid_from
	FROM {{ source('Person-stg', 'stg_Person_Details') }} AS Pn  
	WHERE '{{ var('dbt_BusinessDate') }}' BETWEEN  Pn.dbt_valid_from AND IFNULL(Pn.dbt_valid_to,'2099-06-06')
	AND '{{var('dbt_Layer')}}' = 'stg' AND Pn.dbt_valid_from ='{{var('dbt_BusinessDate')}}'   
	--
	UNION ALL
	--
	SELECT EA.stg_BusinessEntity_key AS stg_BusinessEntity_key, EA.dbt_valid_from
	FROM {{ source('Person-stg', 'stg_Person_EmailAddress') }} AS EA
	WHERE '{{ var('dbt_BusinessDate') }}' BETWEEN  EA.dbt_valid_from AND IFNULL(EA.dbt_valid_to,'2099-06-06')
	AND '{{var('dbt_Layer')}}' = 'stg' AND EA.dbt_valid_from ='{{var('dbt_BusinessDate')}}'  
	--
	UNION ALL
	--
	SELECT PPe.stg_BusinessEntity_key AS stg_BusinessEntity_key, PPe.dbt_valid_from
	FROM  {{ source('Person-stg', 'stg_Person_PersonPhone') }} AS PPe 
	WHERE '{{ var('dbt_BusinessDate') }}' BETWEEN  PPe.dbt_valid_from AND IFNULL(PPe.dbt_valid_to,'2099-06-06')
	AND '{{var('dbt_Layer')}}' = 'stg' AND PPe.dbt_valid_from ='{{var('dbt_BusinessDate')}}'  
	--
	UNION ALL
	--
	SELECT PPe.stg_BusinessEntity_key AS stg_BusinessEntity_key, PPe.dbt_valid_from
	FROM {{ source('Person-stg', 'stg_Person_PersonPhone') }} AS PPe
	JOIN {{ source('Person-stg', 'stg_Person_PhoneNumberType') }} AS PNT 
	ON PPe.stg_PhoneNumberType_key = PNT.stg_PhoneNumberType_key 
	WHERE '{{ var('dbt_BusinessDate') }}' BETWEEN  PPe.dbt_valid_from AND IFNULL(PPe.dbt_valid_to,'2099-06-06') 
	AND '{{ var('dbt_BusinessDate') }}' BETWEEN  PNT.dbt_valid_from AND IFNULL(PNT.dbt_valid_to,'2099-06-06')
	AND '{{var('dbt_Layer')}}' = 'stg' AND PNT.dbt_valid_from ='{{var('dbt_BusinessDate')}}'  
	)

SELECT stg_BusinessEntity_key, max(dbt_valid_from) as dbt_valid_from
FROM DL
GROUP BY stg_BusinessEntity_key

snapshot.ad_lite.fact_Purchasing_OrderDe.name: fact_Purchasing_OrderDetail
snapshot.ad_lite.fact_Purchasing_OrderDe.raw_code:
{{
	config(
		target_database=var('gcp_Project'),
		target_schema=var('gcp_DataSet_baw'),
		strategy='check',		
		unique_key='baw_PurchaseOrderDetail_key',
		cluster_by = 'baw_Product_key',	
		updated_at='ModifiedDate',		
		check_cols=['Purchase_OrderDate','PurchaseShip_Date','PO_Status','PO_RevisionNumber','Line_DueDate','IsProduct','IsTax'
					,'IsFreight','LineOrder_Qty','LineUnit_Price','LineTotal_Price','LineTotal_ReceivedQty','LineTotal_RejectedQty','LineTotal_StockedQty'	
		],
	)
}}


SELECT 
	FARM_FINGERPRINT(CONCAT(POD.stg_composite_key, REPLACE('{{ var('dbt_BusinessDate') }}','-',''))) as baw_PurchaseOrderDetail_key,
	POD.stg_composite_key,
    Pt.baw_Product_key,
	E.baw_Employee_key,
	V.baw_Purchasing_Vendor_key,
	SR.baw_ShipMethod_key,

	POH.OrderDate AS Purchase_OrderDate,
	POH.ShipDate AS PurchaseShip_Date,
	POH.Status AS PO_Status,
	POH.RevisionNumber AS PO_RevisionNumber,
	POD.DueDate AS Line_DueDate,
	1 as IsProduct,
	0 as IsTax,
	0 as IsFreight,
	POD.OrderQty AS LineOrder_Qty,
	POD.UnitPrice AS LineUnit_Price,
	POD.LineTotal AS LineTotal_Price,
	POD.ReceivedQty AS LineTotal_ReceivedQty,
	POD.RejectedQty AS LineTotal_RejectedQty,
	POD.StockedQty AS LineTotal_StockedQty,
	'{{ var('dbt_BusinessDate') }}' AS ModifiedDate
FROM {{ ref('stg_Purchasing_PurchaseOrderDetail') }} AS POD
JOIN {{ ref('stg_Purchasing_PurchaseOrderHeader') }} AS POH 
	ON POD.stg_PurchaseOrder_key=POH.stg_PurchaseOrder_key 
	AND '{{var('dbt_BusinessDate')}}' BETWEEN  POH.dbt_valid_from AND IFNULL(POH.dbt_valid_to,'2099-06-06') 
JOIN  {{ ref('dim2_Common_Product') }} AS Pt 
	ON POD.stg_Product_key=Pt.stg_Product_key  
	AND '{{ var('dbt_BusinessDate') }}' BETWEEN  Pt.dbt_valid_from AND IFNULL(Pt.dbt_valid_to,'2099-06-06') 
JOIN {{ ref('dim2_HumanResources_Employee') }} AS E
	ON POH.stg_Employee_key=E.stg_BusinessEntity_key 
	AND '{{var('dbt_BusinessDate')}}' BETWEEN  E.dbt_valid_from AND IFNULL(E.dbt_valid_to,'2099-06-06') 
JOIN {{ ref('dim2_Purchasing_Vendor') }} AS V 
	ON POH.stg_Vendor_key=V.stg_BusinessEntity_key 
	AND '{{var('dbt_BusinessDate')}}' BETWEEN  V.dbt_valid_from AND IFNULL(V.dbt_valid_to,'2099-06-06')
JOIN {{ ref('dim_Purchasing_ShipMethod') }} AS SR
	ON POH.stg_ShipMethod_key=SR.stg_ShipMethod_key /*SCD TYPE 1*/
WHERE '{{var('dbt_BusinessDate')}}' BETWEEN POD.dbt_valid_from AND IFNULL(POD.dbt_valid_to,'2099-06-06') 
	AND '{{var('dbt_Layer')}}' = 'baw'  
	AND (POH.dbt_valid_from ='{{var('dbt_BusinessDate')}}'  
		OR POD.dbt_valid_from ='{{var('dbt_BusinessDate')}}' )		
---------
UNION ALL
---------
SELECT FARM_FINGERPRINT(CONCAT(POH.stg_PurchaseOrder_key,'FREIGHT', REPLACE('{{ var('dbt_BusinessDate') }}','-',''))) as baw_PurchaseOrderDetail_key,

	'{{ var('dbt_BusinessDate') }}' AS ModifiedDate
FROM {{ ref('stg_Purchasing_PurchaseOrderHeader') }} AS POH 
JOIN {{ ref('dim2_HumanResources_Employee') }} AS E
	ON POH.stg_Employee_key=E.stg_BusinessEntity_key 
	AND '{{var('dbt_BusinessDate')}}' BETWEEN  E.dbt_valid_from AND IFNULL(E.dbt_valid_to,'2099-06-06') 
JOIN {{ ref('dim2_Purchasing_Vendor') }} AS V

JOIN {{ ref('dim_Purchasing_ShipMethod') }} AS SR

	stg_PurchaseOrder_key AS stg_composite_key,
    0 as baw_Product_key, /*Not a Product*/
	E.baw_Employee_key,
	V.baw_Purchasing_Vendor_key,
	SR.baw_ShipMethod_key,

	POH.OrderDate AS Purchase_OrderDate,
	POH.ShipDate AS PurchaseShip_Date,
	POH.Status AS PO_Status,
	POH.RevisionNumber AS PO_RevisionNumber,
	null AS Line_DueDate,
	0 as IsProduct,
	0 as IsTax,
	1 as IsFreight,
	0 AS LineOrder_Qty,
	POH.Freight AS LineUnit_Price,
	POH.Freight AS LineTotal_Price,
	0 AS LineTotal_ReceivedQty,
	0 AS LineTotal_RejectedQty,
	0 AS LineTotal_StockedQty,
	'2011-06-01' AS ModifiedDate
FROM `sample-project`.`adventureworks_stg_ds`.`stg_Purchasing_PurchaseOrderHeader` AS POH 
JOIN `sample-project`.`adventureworks_baw_ds`.`dim2_HumanResources_Employee` AS E
	ON POH.stg_Employee_key=E.stg_BusinessEntity_key 
	AND '2011-06-01' BETWEEN  E.dbt_valid_from AND IFNULL(E.dbt_valid_to,'2099-06-06') 
JOIN `sample-project`.`adventureworks_baw_ds`.`dim2_Purchasing_Vendor` AS V 
	ON POH.stg_Vendor_key=V.stg_BusinessEntity_key 
	AND '2011-06-01' BETWEEN  V.dbt_valid_from AND IFNULL(V.dbt_valid_to,'2099-06-06') 
JOIN `sample-project`.`adventureworks_baw_ds`.`dim_Purchasing_ShipMethod` AS SR
	ON POH.stg_ShipMethod_key=SR.stg_ShipMethod_key /*SCD TYPE 1*/
WHERE '2011-06-01' BETWEEN POH.dbt_valid_from AND IFNULL(POH.dbt_valid_to,'2099-06-06') 
	AND 'raw' = 'baw'  
	AND POH.dbt_valid_from ='2011-06-01'  

---------
UNION ALL
---------
SELECT FARM_FINGERPRINT(CONCAT(POH.stg_PurchaseOrder_key,'TAX', REPLACE('2011-06-01','-',''))) as baw_PurchaseOrderDetail_key, 
	stg_PurchaseOrder_key AS stg_composite_key,
	0 as baw_Product_key, /*Not a Product*/
	E.baw_Employee_key,
	V.baw_Purchasing_Vendor_key ,
	SR.baw_ShipMethod_key,

	POH.OrderDate AS Purchase_OrderDate,
	POH.ShipDate AS PurchaseShip_Date,
	POH.Status AS PO_Status,
	POH.RevisionNumber AS PO_RevisionNumber,

	null AS Line_DueDate,
	0 as IsProduct,
	1 as IsTax,
	0 as IsFreight,
	0 AS LineOrder_Qty,
	POH.TaxAmt AS LineUnit_Price,
	POH.TaxAmt AS LineTotal_Price,
	0 AS LineTotal_ReceivedQty,
	0 AS LineTotal_RejectedQty,
	0 AS LineTotal_StockedQty,
	'2011-06-01' AS ModifiedDate
FROM `sample-project`.`adventureworks_stg_ds`.`stg_Purchasing_PurchaseOrderHeader` AS POH 
JOIN `sample-project`.`adventureworks_baw_ds`.`dim2_HumanResources_Employee` AS E
	ON POH.stg_Employee_key=E.stg_BusinessEntity_key 
	AND '2011-06-01' BETWEEN  E.dbt_valid_from AND IFNULL(E.dbt_valid_to,'2099-06-06') 
JOIN `sample-project`.`adventureworks_baw_ds`.`dim2_Purchasing_Vendor` AS V 
	ON POH.stg_Vendor_key=V.stg_BusinessEntity_key 
	AND '2011-06-01' BETWEEN  V.dbt_valid_from AND IFNULL(V.dbt_valid_to,'2099-06-06') 
JOIN `sample-project`.`adventureworks_baw_ds`.`dim_Purchasing_ShipMethod` AS SR
	ON POH.stg_ShipMethod_key=SR.stg_ShipMethod_key /*SCD TYPE 1*/
WHERE '2011-06-01' BETWEEN POH.dbt_valid_from AND IFNULL(POH.dbt_valid_to,'2099-06-06') 
	AND 'raw' = 'baw'  
	AND POH.dbt_valid_from ='2011-06-01'

snapshot.ad_lite.dim2_Purchasing_Vendor.name: dim2_Purchasing_Vendor
snapshot.ad_lite.dim2_Purchasing_Vendor.raw_code:
{{
	config(
		target_database=var('gcp_Project'),
		target_schema=var('gcp_DataSet_baw'),
		strategy='check',		
		unique_key='stg_BusinessEntity_key',
		cluster_by = 'stg_BusinessEntity_key',			
		updated_at='ModifiedDate',
		check_cols=['ContactType','PersonTitle', 'AdditionalContactInfo', 'ContactDemographicsXML','PersonType','NameStyle','FirstName','MiddleName',
					'LastName', 'Suffix', 'EmailPromotion','Current_EmailAddress','WorkPhone','HomePhone','MobilePhone',
					'AccountNumber', 'VendorName', 'VendorCreditRating', 'VendorCreditStatus', 'IsVendorActive', 'PurchasingWebServiceURL','VendorProductName_List'
					],
	)
}}
WITH VNL AS (
		SELECT PV.stg_BusinessEntity_key , 
		  CONCAT("'",STRING_AGG(DISTINCT REPLACE(Pt.Name,' & ', ' AND '), "' & '") ,"'") AS VendorProductName_List
		FROM {{ ref('stg_Purchasing_ProductVendor') }} AS PV
		JOIN {{ ref('stg_Build_Product') }} AS Pt 
			ON PV.stg_Product_key =Pt.stg_Product_key
		JOIN {{ ref('dl_dim2_Purchasing_Vendor') }} AS ddl
			ON PV.stg_BusinessEntity_key = ddl.stg_BusinessEntity_key	
			AND PV.dbt_valid_from = ddl.dbt_valid_from
		WHERE  '{{ var('dbt_BusinessDate') }}' BETWEEN  PV.dbt_valid_from AND IFNULL(PV.dbt_valid_to,'2099-06-06') 	
			AND '{{ var('dbt_BusinessDate') }}' BETWEEN  Pt.dbt_valid_from AND IFNULL(Pt.dbt_valid_to,'2099-06-06') 
		GROUP BY PV.stg_BusinessEntity_key
		)


SELECT 
	FARM_FINGERPRINT(CONCAT(V.stg_BusinessEntity_key, REPLACE('{{ var('dbt_BusinessDate') }}','-',''))) as baw_Purchasing_Vendor_key,
	V.stg_BusinessEntity_key,
	CT.Name AS ContactType,
	IFNULL(Pn.Title,'') AS PersonTitle,Pn.AdditionalContactInfo,Pn.Demographics AS ContactDemographicsXML,
	Pn.PersonType,Pn.NameStyle,Pn.FirstName,IFNULL(Pn.MiddleName,'') AS MiddleName,Pn.LastName,IFNULL(Pn.Suffix,'') AS Suffix,Pn.EmailPromotion,
	FIRST_VALUE(EA.EmailAddress) OVER (PARTITION BY EA.stg_BusinessEntity_key ORDER BY EA.ModifiedDate DESC, EA.stg_composite_key DESC) AS Current_EmailAddress, 
	FIRST_VALUE(CASE WHEN PNT1.Name IS NULL THEN '' ELSE PPe1.PhoneNumber END) OVER (PARTITION BY PPe1.stg_BusinessEntity_key ORDER BY PPe1.ModifiedDate DESC, PPe1.PhoneNumber DESC) AS WorkPhone,
	FIRST_VALUE(CASE WHEN PNT2.Name IS NULL THEN '' ELSE PPe2.PhoneNumber END) OVER (PARTITION BY PPe2.stg_BusinessEntity_key ORDER BY PPe2.ModifiedDate DESC, PPe2.PhoneNumber DESC) AS HomePhone,
	FIRST_VALUE(CASE WHEN PNT3.Name IS NULL THEN '' ELSE PPe3.PhoneNumber END) OVER (PARTITION BY PPe3.stg_BusinessEntity_key ORDER BY PPe3.ModifiedDate DESC, PPe3.PhoneNumber DESC) AS MobilePhone,
	V.AccountNumber, V.Name AS VendorName, V.CreditRating AS VendorCreditRating, 
	V.PreferredVendorStatus AS VendorCreditStatus, 
	V.ActiveFlag AS IsVendorActive, 
	V.PurchasingWebServiceURL,
	COALESCE(VNL.VendorProductName_List,'*UNKNOWN*') AS VendorProductName_List,
	'{{ var('dbt_BusinessDate') }}' AS ModifiedDate
 FROM {{ ref('stg_Purchasing_Vendor') }} AS V
 JOIN {{ ref('dl_dim2_Purchasing_Vendor') }} AS ddl
	ON V.stg_BusinessEntity_key = ddl.stg_BusinessEntity_key
	AND V.dbt_valid_from = ddl.dbt_valid_from
JOIN {{ ref('stg_Person_BusinessEntityContact') }} AS Bec 
	ON V.stg_BusinessEntity_key	=Bec.stg_BusinessEntity_key AND '{{ var('dbt_BusinessDate') }}' BETWEEN  Bec.dbt_valid_from AND IFNULL(Bec.dbt_valid_to,'2099-06-06') 	
JOIN {{ ref('stg_Person_ContactType') }} AS CT
	ON CT.stg_ContactType_key	=Bec.stg_ContactType_key AND '{{ var('dbt_BusinessDate') }}' BETWEEN  CT.dbt_valid_from AND IFNULL(CT.dbt_valid_to,'2099-06-06') 	
JOIN {{ ref('stg_Person_Details') }} AS Pn 
	ON Bec.stg_Person_key	=Pn.stg_BusinessEntity_key AND '{{ var('dbt_BusinessDate') }}' BETWEEN  Pn.dbt_valid_from AND IFNULL(Pn.dbt_valid_to,'2099-06-06') 
	/*SNAPSHOT NOT REQUIRED AS QUALIFY STATEMENT LIMITS THIS: AND '{{ var('dbt_BusinessDate') }}' BETWEEN  Pn.dbt_valid_from AND IFNULL(Pn.dbt_valid_to,'2099-06-06')*/
LEFT JOIN {{ ref('stg_Person_EmailAddress') }} AS EA 
	ON Pn.stg_BusinessEntity_key	 = EA.stg_BusinessEntity_key AND '{{ var('dbt_BusinessDate') }}' BETWEEN  EA.dbt_valid_from AND IFNULL(EA.dbt_valid_to,'2099-06-06') 
LEFT JOIN {{ ref('stg_Person_PersonPhone') }} AS PPe1 
	ON PPe1.stg_BusinessEntity_key	 = Pn.stg_BusinessEntity_key AND '{{ var('dbt_BusinessDate') }}' BETWEEN  PPe1.dbt_valid_from AND IFNULL(PPe1.dbt_valid_to,'2099-06-06') 	
LEFT JOIN {{ ref('stg_Person_PhoneNumberType') }} AS PNT1 
	ON PPe1.stg_BusinessEntity_key = PNT1.stg_PhoneNumberType_key AND PNT1.Name = 'Work' AND '{{ var('dbt_BusinessDate') }}' BETWEEN  PNT1.dbt_valid_from AND IFNULL(PNT1.dbt_valid_to,'2099-06-06') 
LEFT JOIN {{ ref('stg_Person_PersonPhone') }} AS PPe2 
	ON PPe2.stg_BusinessEntity_key	 = Pn.stg_BusinessEntity_key  AND '{{ var('dbt_BusinessDate') }}' BETWEEN  PPe2.dbt_valid_from AND IFNULL(PPe2.dbt_valid_to,'2099-06-06') 	
LEFT JOIN {{ ref('stg_Person_PhoneNumberType') }} AS PNT2 
	ON PPe2.stg_PhoneNumberType_key=PNT2.stg_PhoneNumberType_key AND PNT2.Name = 'Home'  AND '{{ var('dbt_BusinessDate') }}' BETWEEN  PNT2.dbt_valid_from AND IFNULL(PNT2.dbt_valid_to,'2099-06-06') 
LEFT JOIN {{ ref('stg_Person_PersonPhone') }} AS PPe3 
	ON PPe3.stg_BusinessEntity_key	 = Pn.stg_BusinessEntity_key  AND '{{ var('dbt_BusinessDate') }}' BETWEEN  PPe3.dbt_valid_from AND IFNULL(PPe3.dbt_valid_to,'2099-06-06') 	
LEFT JOIN {{ ref('stg_Person_PhoneNumberType') }} AS PNT3 
	ON PPe3.stg_PhoneNumberType_key=PNT3.stg_PhoneNumberType_key AND PNT3.Name = 'Cell'  AND '{{ var('dbt_BusinessDate') }}' BETWEEN  PNT3.dbt_valid_from AND IFNULL(PNT3.dbt_valid_to,'2099-06-06')  
LEFT JOIN VNL
	ON V.stg_BusinessEntity_key =  VNL.stg_BusinessEntity_key
WHERE '{{var('dbt_Layer')}}' = 'baw' AND V.dbt_valid_from ='{{var('dbt_BusinessDate')}}'  
QUALIFY ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY V.stg_BusinessEntity_key ORDER BY  Pn.ModifiedDate DESC, EA.ModifiedDate DESC, PPe1.ModifiedDate DESC, PPe2.ModifiedDate DESC, PPe3.ModifiedDate DESC) = 1

macro.dbt_bigquery.bigquery__get_catalog.macro_sql:
{% macro bigquery__get_catalog(information_schema, schemas) -%}

  {%- if (schemas | length) == 0 -%}
    {# Hopefully nothing cares about the columns we return when there are no rows #}
    {%- set query  = "select 1 as id limit 0" -%}
  {%- else -%}

  {%- set query -%}
    with tables as (
        select
            project_id as table_database,
            dataset_id as table_schema,
            table_id as original_table_name,

            concat(project_id, '.', dataset_id, '.', table_id) as relation_id,

            row_count,
            size_bytes as size_bytes,
            case
                when type = 1 then 'table'
                when type = 2 then 'view'
                else 'external'
            end as table_type,

            REGEXP_CONTAINS(table_id, '^.+[0-9]{8}$') and coalesce(type, 0) = 1 as is_date_shard,
            REGEXP_EXTRACT(table_id, '^(.+)[0-9]{8}$') as shard_base_name,
            REGEXP_EXTRACT(table_id, '^.+([0-9]{8})$') as shard_name

        from {{ information_schema.replace(information_schema_view='__TABLES__') }}
        where (
          {%- for schema in schemas -%}
            upper(dataset_id) = upper('{{ schema }}'){%- if not loop.last %} or {% endif -%}
          {%- endfor -%}
        )
    ),

    table_options as (
        select
            concat(table_catalog, '.', table_schema, '.', table_name) as relation_id,
            JSON_VALUE(option_value) as table_comment

        from {{ information_schema.replace(information_schema_view='TABLE_OPTIONS') }}
        where option_name = 'description'
    ),
    extracted as (

        select *,
            case
                when is_date_shard then shard_base_name
                else original_table_name
            end as table_name

        from tables

    ),

    unsharded_tables as (

        select
            table_database,
            table_schema,
            table_name,
            coalesce(table_type, 'external') as table_type,
            is_date_shard,

            struct(
                min(shard_name) as shard_min,
                max(shard_name) as shard_max,
                count(*) as shard_count
            ) as table_shards,

            sum(size_bytes) as size_bytes,
            sum(row_count) as row_count,

            max(relation_id) as relation_id

        from extracted
        group by 1,2,3,4,5

    ),

    info_schema_columns as (

        select
            concat(table_catalog, '.', table_schema, '.', table_name) as relation_id,
            table_catalog as table_database,
            table_schema,
            table_name,

            -- use the "real" column name from the paths query below
            column_name as base_column_name,
            ordinal_position as column_index,

            is_partitioning_column,
            clustering_ordinal_position

        from {{ information_schema.replace(information_schema_view='COLUMNS') }}
        where ordinal_position is not null

    ),

    info_schema_column_paths as (

        select
            concat(table_catalog, '.', table_schema, '.', table_name) as relation_id,
            field_path as column_name,
            data_type as column_type,
            column_name as base_column_name,
            description as column_comment

        from {{ information_schema.replace(information_schema_view='COLUMN_FIELD_PATHS') }}

    ),

    columns as (

        select * except (base_column_name)
        from info_schema_columns
        join info_schema_column_paths using (relation_id, base_column_name)

    ),

    column_stats as (

        select
            table_database,
            table_schema,
            table_name,
            max(relation_id) as relation_id,
            max(case when is_partitioning_column = 'YES' then 1 else 0 end) = 1 as is_partitioned,
            max(case when is_partitioning_column = 'YES' then column_name else null end) as partition_column,
            max(case when clustering_ordinal_position is not null then 1 else 0 end) = 1 as is_clustered,
            array_to_string(
                array_agg(
                    case
                        when clustering_ordinal_position is not null then column_name
                        else null
                    end ignore nulls
                    order by clustering_ordinal_position
                ), ', '
            ) as clustering_columns

        from columns
        group by 1,2,3

    )

    select
        unsharded_tables.table_database,
        unsharded_tables.table_schema,
        case
            when is_date_shard then concat(unsharded_tables.table_name, '*')
            else unsharded_tables.table_name
        end as table_name,
        unsharded_tables.table_type,
        table_options.table_comment,

        -- coalesce name and type for External tables - these columns are not
        -- present in the COLUMN_FIELD_PATHS resultset
        coalesce(columns.column_name, '<unknown>') as column_name,
        -- invent a row number to account for nested fields -- BQ does
        -- not treat these nested properties as independent fields
        row_number() over (
            partition by relation_id
            order by columns.column_index, columns.column_name
        ) as column_index,
        coalesce(columns.column_type, '<unknown>') as column_type,
        columns.column_comment,

        'Shard count' as `stats__date_shards__label`,
        table_shards.shard_count as `stats__date_shards__value`,
        'The number of date shards in this table' as `stats__date_shards__description`,
        is_date_shard as `stats__date_shards__include`,

        'Shard (min)' as `stats__date_shard_min__label`,
        table_shards.shard_min as `stats__date_shard_min__value`,
        'The first date shard in this table' as `stats__date_shard_min__description`,
        is_date_shard as `stats__date_shard_min__include`,

        'Shard (max)' as `stats__date_shard_max__label`,
        table_shards.shard_max as `stats__date_shard_max__value`,
        'The last date shard in this table' as `stats__date_shard_max__description`,
        is_date_shard as `stats__date_shard_max__include`,

        '# Rows' as `stats__num_rows__label`,
        row_count as `stats__num_rows__value`,
        'Approximate count of rows in this table' as `stats__num_rows__description`,
        (unsharded_tables.table_type = 'table') as `stats__num_rows__include`,

        'Approximate Size' as `stats__num_bytes__label`,
        size_bytes as `stats__num_bytes__value`,
        'Approximate size of table as reported by BigQuery' as `stats__num_bytes__description`,
        (unsharded_tables.table_type = 'table') as `stats__num_bytes__include`,

        'Partitioned By' as `stats__partitioning_type__label`,
        partition_column as `stats__partitioning_type__value`,
        'The partitioning column for this table' as `stats__partitioning_type__description`,
        is_partitioned as `stats__partitioning_type__include`,

        'Clustered By' as `stats__clustering_fields__label`,
        clustering_columns as `stats__clustering_fields__value`,
        'The clustering columns for this table' as `stats__clustering_fields__description`,
        is_clustered as `stats__clustering_fields__include`

    -- join using relation_id (an actual relation, not a shard prefix) to make
    -- sure that column metadata is picked up through the join. This will only
    -- return the column information for the "max" table in a date-sharded table set
    from unsharded_tables
    left join table_options using (relation_id)
    left join columns using (relation_id)
    left join column_stats using (relation_id)
  {%- endset -%}

  {%- endif -%}

  {{ return(run_query(query)) }}

{%- endmacro %}

macro.dbt_bigquery.py_write_table.macro_sql:
{% macro py_write_table(compiled_code, target_relation) %}
from pyspark.sql import SparkSession

spark = SparkSession.builder.appName('smallTest').getOrCreate()

spark.conf.set("viewsEnabled","true")
spark.conf.set("temporaryGcsBucket","{{target.gcs_bucket}}")

{{ compiled_code }}
dbt = dbtObj(spark.read.format("bigquery").load)
df = model(dbt, spark)

# COMMAND ----------
# this is materialization code dbt generated, please do not modify

import pyspark
# make sure pandas exists before using it
try:
  import pandas
  pandas_available = True
except ImportError:
  pandas_available = False

# make sure pyspark.pandas exists before using it
try:
  import pyspark.pandas
  pyspark_pandas_api_available = True
except ImportError:
  pyspark_pandas_api_available = False

# make sure databricks.koalas exists before using it
try:
  import databricks.koalas
  koalas_available = True
except ImportError:
  koalas_available = False

# preferentially convert pandas DataFrames to pandas-on-Spark or Koalas DataFrames first
# since they know how to convert pandas DataFrames better than `spark.createDataFrame(df)`
# and converting from pandas-on-Spark to Spark DataFrame has no overhead
if pyspark_pandas_api_available and pandas_available and isinstance(df, pandas.core.frame.DataFrame):
  df = pyspark.pandas.frame.DataFrame(df)
elif koalas_available and pandas_available and isinstance(df, pandas.core.frame.DataFrame):
  df = databricks.koalas.frame.DataFrame(df)

# convert to pyspark.sql.dataframe.DataFrame
if isinstance(df, pyspark.sql.dataframe.DataFrame):
  pass  # since it is already a Spark DataFrame
elif pyspark_pandas_api_available and isinstance(df, pyspark.pandas.frame.DataFrame):
  df = df.to_spark()
elif koalas_available and isinstance(df, databricks.koalas.frame.DataFrame):
  df = df.to_spark()
elif pandas_available and isinstance(df, pandas.core.frame.DataFrame):
  df = spark.createDataFrame(df)
else:
  msg = f"{type(df)} is not a supported type for dbt Python materialization"
  raise Exception(msg)

df.write \
  .mode("overwrite") \
  .format("bigquery") \
  .option("writeMethod", "direct").option("writeDisposition", 'WRITE_TRUNCATE') \
  .save("{{target_relation}}")
{% endmacro %}

macro.dbt.default__snapshot_staging_tabl.macro_sql:
{% macro default__snapshot_staging_table(strategy, source_sql, target_relation) -%}

    with snapshot_query as (

        {{ source_sql }}

    ),

    snapshotted_data as (

        select *,
            {{ strategy.unique_key }} as dbt_unique_key

        from {{ target_relation }}
        where dbt_valid_to is null

    ),

    insertions_source_data as (

        select
            *,
            {{ strategy.unique_key }} as dbt_unique_key,
            {{ strategy.updated_at }} as dbt_updated_at,
            {{ strategy.updated_at }} as dbt_valid_from,
            nullif({{ strategy.updated_at }}, {{ strategy.updated_at }}) as dbt_valid_to,
            {{ strategy.scd_id }} as dbt_scd_id

        from snapshot_query
    ),

    updates_source_data as (

        select
            *,
            {{ strategy.unique_key }} as dbt_unique_key,
            {{ strategy.updated_at }} as dbt_updated_at,
            {{ strategy.updated_at }} as dbt_valid_from,
            {{ strategy.updated_at }} as dbt_valid_to

        from snapshot_query
    ),

    {%- if strategy.invalidate_hard_deletes %}

    deletes_source_data as (

        select
            *,
            {{ strategy.unique_key }} as dbt_unique_key
        from snapshot_query
    ),
    {% endif %}

    insertions as (

        select
            'insert' as dbt_change_type,
            source_data.*

        from insertions_source_data as source_data
        left outer join snapshotted_data on snapshotted_data.dbt_unique_key = source_data.dbt_unique_key
        where snapshotted_data.dbt_unique_key is null
           or (
                snapshotted_data.dbt_unique_key is not null
            and (
                {{ strategy.row_changed }}
            )
        )

    ),

    updates as (

        select
            'update' as dbt_change_type,
            source_data.*,
            snapshotted_data.dbt_scd_id

        from updates_source_data as source_data
        join snapshotted_data on snapshotted_data.dbt_unique_key = source_data.dbt_unique_key
        where (
            {{ strategy.row_changed }}
        )
    )

    {%- if strategy.invalidate_hard_deletes -%}
    ,

    deletes as (

        select
            'delete' as dbt_change_type,
            source_data.*,
            {{ snapshot_get_time() }} as dbt_valid_from,
            {{ snapshot_get_time() }} as dbt_updated_at,
            {{ snapshot_get_time() }} as dbt_valid_to,
            snapshotted_data.dbt_scd_id

        from snapshotted_data
        left join deletes_source_data as source_data on snapshotted_data.dbt_unique_key = source_data.dbt_unique_key
        where source_data.dbt_unique_key is null
    )
    {%- endif %}

    select * from insertions
    union all
    select * from updates
    {%- if strategy.invalidate_hard_deletes %}
    union all
    select * from deletes
    {%- endif %}

{%- endmacro %}

{% macro default__snapshot_merge_sql(target, source, insert_cols) -%}
    {%- set insert_cols_csv = insert_cols | join(', ') -%}

    merge into {{ target }} as DBT_INTERNAL_DEST
    using {{ source }} as DBT_INTERNAL_SOURCE
    on DBT_INTERNAL_SOURCE.dbt_scd_id = DBT_INTERNAL_DEST.dbt_scd_id

    when matched
     and DBT_INTERNAL_DEST.dbt_valid_to is null
     and DBT_INTERNAL_SOURCE.dbt_change_type in ('update', 'delete')
        then update
        set dbt_valid_to = DBT_INTERNAL_SOURCE.dbt_valid_to

    when not matched
     and DBT_INTERNAL_SOURCE.dbt_change_type = 'insert'
        then insert ({{ insert_cols_csv }})
        values ({{ insert_cols_csv }})

macro.audit_helper.default__compare_colu.name: default__compare_column_values
macro.audit_helper.default__compare_colu.macro_sql:
{% macro default__compare_column_values(a_query, b_query, primary_key, column_to_compare) -%}
with a_query as (
    {{ a_query }}
),

b_query as (
    {{ b_query }}
),

joined as (
    select
        coalesce(a_query.{{ primary_key }}, b_query.{{ primary_key }}) as {{ primary_key }},
        a_query.{{ column_to_compare }} as a_query_value,
        b_query.{{ column_to_compare }} as b_query_value,
        case
            when a_query.{{ column_to_compare }} = b_query.{{ column_to_compare }} then ': perfect match'
            when a_query.{{ column_to_compare }} is null and b_query.{{ column_to_compare }} is null then ': both are null'
            when a_query.{{ primary_key }} is null then ': missing from a'
            when b_query.{{ primary_key }} is null then ': missing from b'
            when a_query.{{ column_to_compare }} is null then ': value is null in a only'
            when b_query.{{ column_to_compare }} is null then ': value is null in b only'
            when a_query.{{ column_to_compare }} != b_query.{{ column_to_compare }} then ': values do not match'
            else 'unknown' -- this should never happen
        end as match_status,
        case
            when a_query.{{ column_to_compare }} = b_query.{{ column_to_compare }} then 0
            when a_query.{{ column_to_compare }} is null and b_query.{{ column_to_compare }} is null then 1
            when a_query.{{ primary_key }} is null then 2
            when b_query.{{ primary_key }} is null then 3
            when a_query.{{ column_to_compare }} is null then 4
            when b_query.{{ column_to_compare }} is null then 5
            when a_query.{{ column_to_compare }} != b_query.{{ column_to_compare }} then 6
            else 7 -- this should never happen
        end as match_order

    from a_query

    full outer join b_query on a_query.{{ primary_key }} = b_query.{{ primary_key }}
),

aggregated as (
    select
        '{{ column_to_compare }}' as column_name,
        match_status,
        match_order,
        count(*) as count_records
    from joined

    group by column_name, match_status, match_order
)

select
    column_name,
    match_status,
    count_records,
    round(100.0 * count_records / sum(count_records) over (), 2) as percent_of_total

from aggregated

order by match_order

{% endmacro %}

macro.audit_helper.default__compare_quer.macro_sql:
{% macro default__compare_queries(a_query, b_query, primary_key=None, summarize=true) %}

with a as (

    {{ a_query }}

),

b as (

    {{ b_query }}

),

a_intersect_b as (

    select * from a
    {{ dbt.intersect() }}
    select * from b

),

a_except_b as (

    select * from a
    {{ dbt.except() }}
    select * from b

),

b_except_a as (

    select * from b
    {{ dbt.except() }}
    select * from a

),

all_records as (

    select
        *,
        true as in_a,
        true as in_b
    from a_intersect_b

    union all

    select
        *,
        true as in_a,
        false as in_b
    from a_except_b

    union all

    select
        *,
        false as in_a,
        true as in_b
    from b_except_a

),

{%- if summarize %}

summary_stats as (

    select

        in_a,
        in_b,
        count(*) as count

    from all_records
    group by 1, 2

),

final as (

    select

        *,
        round(100.0 * count / sum(count) over (), 2) as percent_of_total

    from summary_stats
    order by in_a desc, in_b desc

)

{%- else %}

final as (
    
    select * from all_records
    where not (in_a and in_b)
    order by {{ primary_key ~ ", " if primary_key is not none }} in_a desc, in_b desc

)

{%- endif %}

select * from final

{% endmacro %}

{% macro default__get_date_dimension(start_date, end_date) %}
with base_dates as (
    {{ dbt_date.get_base_dates(start_date, end_date) }}
),
dates_with_prior_year_dates as (

    select
        cast(d.date_day as date) as date_day,
        cast({{ dbt.dateadd('year', -1 , 'd.date_day') }} as date) as prior_year_date_day,
        cast({{ dbt.dateadd('day', -364 , 'd.date_day') }} as date) as prior_year_over_year_date_day
    from
    	base_dates d

)
select
    d.date_day,
    {{ dbt_date.yesterday('d.date_day') }} as prior_date_day,
    {{ dbt_date.tomorrow('d.date_day') }} as next_date_day,
    d.prior_year_date_day as prior_year_date_day,
    d.prior_year_over_year_date_day,
    {{ dbt_date.day_of_week('d.date_day', isoweek=false) }} as day_of_week,
    {{ dbt_date.day_of_week('d.date_day', isoweek=true) }} as day_of_week_iso,
    {{ dbt_date.day_name('d.date_day', short=false) }} as day_of_week_name,
    {{ dbt_date.day_name('d.date_day', short=true) }} as day_of_week_name_short,
    {{ dbt_date.day_of_month('d.date_day') }} as day_of_month,
    {{ dbt_date.day_of_year('d.date_day') }} as day_of_year,

    {{ dbt_date.week_start('d.date_day') }} as week_start_date,
    {{ dbt_date.week_end('d.date_day') }} as week_end_date,
    {{ dbt_date.week_start('d.prior_year_over_year_date_day') }} as prior_year_week_start_date,
    {{ dbt_date.week_end('d.prior_year_over_year_date_day') }} as prior_year_week_end_date,
    {{ dbt_date.week_of_year('d.date_day') }} as week_of_year,

    {{ dbt_date.iso_week_start('d.date_day') }} as iso_week_start_date,
    {{ dbt_date.iso_week_end('d.date_day') }} as iso_week_end_date,
    {{ dbt_date.iso_week_start('d.prior_year_over_year_date_day') }} as prior_year_iso_week_start_date,
    {{ dbt_date.iso_week_end('d.prior_year_over_year_date_day') }} as prior_year_iso_week_end_date,
    {{ dbt_date.iso_week_of_year('d.date_day') }} as iso_week_of_year,

    {{ dbt_date.week_of_year('d.prior_year_over_year_date_day') }} as prior_year_week_of_year,
    {{ dbt_date.iso_week_of_year('d.prior_year_over_year_date_day') }} as prior_year_iso_week_of_year,

    cast({{ dbt_date.date_part('month', 'd.date_day') }} as {{ dbt.type_int() }}) as month_of_year,
    {{ dbt_date.month_name('d.date_day', short=false) }}  as month_name,
    {{ dbt_date.month_name('d.date_day', short=true) }}  as month_name_short,

    cast({{ dbt.date_trunc('month', 'd.date_day') }} as date) as month_start_date,
    cast({{ last_day('d.date_day', 'month') }} as date) as month_end_date,

    cast({{ dbt.date_trunc('month', 'd.prior_year_date_day') }} as date) as prior_year_month_start_date,
    cast({{ last_day('d.prior_year_date_day', 'month') }} as date) as prior_year_month_end_date,

    cast({{ dbt_date.date_part('quarter', 'd.date_day') }} as {{ dbt.type_int() }}) as quarter_of_year,
    cast({{ dbt.date_trunc('quarter', 'd.date_day') }} as date) as quarter_start_date,
    cast({{ last_day('d.date_day', 'quarter') }} as date) as quarter_end_date,

    cast({{ dbt_date.date_part('year', 'd.date_day') }} as {{ dbt.type_int() }}) as year_number,
    cast({{ dbt.date_trunc('year', 'd.date_day') }} as date) as year_start_date,
    cast({{ last_day('d.date_day', 'year') }} as date) as year_end_date
from
    dates_with_prior_year_dates d
order by 1
{% endmacro %}

macro.dbt_date.get_fiscal_periods.name: get_fiscal_periods
macro.dbt_date.get_fiscal_periods.macro_sql:
{% macro get_fiscal_periods(dates, year_end_month, week_start_day, shift_year=1) %}
{#
This macro requires you to pass in a ref to a date dimension, created via
dbt_date.get_date_dimension()s
#}
with fscl_year_dates_for_periods as (
    {{ dbt_date.get_fiscal_year_dates(dates, year_end_month, week_start_day, shift_year) }}
),
fscl_year_w13 as (

    select
        f.*,
        -- We count the weeks in a 13 week period
        -- and separate the 4-5-4 week sequences
        mod(cast(
            (f.fiscal_week_of_year-1) as {{ dbt.type_int() }}
            ), 13) as w13_number,
        -- Chop weeks into 13 week merch quarters
        cast(
            least(
                floor((f.fiscal_week_of_year-1)/13.0)
                , 3)
            as {{ dbt.type_int() }}) as quarter_number
    from
        fscl_year_dates_for_periods f

),
fscl_periods as (

    select
        f.date_day,
        f.fiscal_year_number,
        f.week_start_date,
        f.week_end_date,
        f.fiscal_week_of_year,
        case
            -- we move week 53 into the 3rd period of the quarter
            when f.fiscal_week_of_year = 53 then 3
            when f.w13_number between 0 and 3 then 1
            when f.w13_number between 4 and 8 then 2
            when f.w13_number between 9 and 12 then 3
        end as period_of_quarter,
        f.quarter_number
    from
        fscl_year_w13 f

),
fscl_periods_quarters as (

    select
        f.*,
        cast((
            (f.quarter_number * 3) + f.period_of_quarter
         ) as {{ dbt.type_int() }}) as fiscal_period_number
    from
        fscl_periods f

)
select
    date_day,
    fiscal_year_number,
    week_start_date,
    week_end_date,
    fiscal_week_of_year,
    dense_rank() over(partition by fiscal_period_number order by fiscal_week_of_year) as fiscal_week_of_period,
    fiscal_period_number,
    quarter_number+1 as fiscal_quarter_number,
    period_of_quarter as fiscal_period_of_quarter
from
    fscl_periods_quarters
order by 1,2
{% endmacro %}

macro.dbt_date.get_fiscal_year_dates.name: get_fiscal_year_dates

macro.dbt_date.default__get_fiscal_year_.name: default__get_fiscal_year_dates
macro.dbt_date.default__get_fiscal_year_.macro_sql:
{% macro default__get_fiscal_year_dates(dates, year_end_month, week_start_day, shift_year) %}
-- this gets all the dates within a fiscal year
-- determined by the given year-end-month
-- ending on the saturday closest to that month's end date
with date_dimension as (
    select * from {{ dates }}
),
year_month_end as (

    select
       d.year_number - {{ shift_year }} as fiscal_year_number,
       d.month_end_date
    from
        date_dimension d
    where
        d.month_of_year = {{ year_end_month }}
    group by 1,2

),
weeks as (

    select
        d.year_number,
        d.month_of_year,
        d.date_day as week_start_date,
        cast({{ dbt.dateadd('day', 6, 'd.date_day') }} as date) as week_end_date
    from
        date_dimension d
    where
        d.day_of_week = {{ week_start_day }}

),
-- get all the weeks that start in the month the year ends
year_week_ends as (

    select
        d.year_number - {{ shift_year }} as fiscal_year_number,
        d.week_end_date
    from
        weeks d
    where
        d.month_of_year = {{ year_end_month }}
    group by
        1,2

),
-- then calculate which Saturday is closest to month end
weeks_at_month_end as (

    select
        d.fiscal_year_number,
        d.week_end_date,
        m.month_end_date,
        rank() over
            (partition by d.fiscal_year_number
                order by
                abs({{ dbt.datediff('d.week_end_date', 'm.month_end_date', 'day') }})

            ) as closest_to_month_end
    from
        year_week_ends d
        join
        year_month_end m on d.fiscal_year_number = m.fiscal_year_number
),
fiscal_year_range as (

    select
        w.fiscal_year_number,
        cast(
            {{ dbt.dateadd('day', 1,
            'lag(w.week_end_date) over(order by w.week_end_date)') }}
            as date) as fiscal_year_start_date,
        w.week_end_date as fiscal_year_end_date
    from
        weeks_at_month_end w
    where
        w.closest_to_month_end = 1

),
fiscal_year_dates as (

    select
        d.date_day,
        m.fiscal_year_number,
        m.fiscal_year_start_date,
        m.fiscal_year_end_date,
        w.week_start_date,
        w.week_end_date,
        -- we reset the weeks of the year starting with the merch year start date
        dense_rank()
            over(
                partition by m.fiscal_year_number
                order by w.week_start_date
                ) as fiscal_week_of_year
    from
        date_dimension d
        join
        fiscal_year_range m on d.date_day between m.fiscal_year_start_date and m.fiscal_year_end_date
        join
        weeks w on d.date_day between w.week_start_date and w.week_end_date

)
select * from fiscal_year_dates order by 1
{% endmacro %}

macro.dbt_expectations.test_expect_colum.macro_sql:
{% test expect_column_values_to_have_consistent_casing(model, column_name, display_inconsistent_columns=False) %}

with test_data as (

    select
        distinct {{ column_name }} as distinct_values
    from
        {{ model }}

 ),
 {% if display_inconsistent_columns %}
 validation_errors as (

    select
        lower(distinct_values) as inconsistent_columns,
        count(distinct_values) as set_count_case_insensitive
    from
        test_data
    group by 1
    having
        count(distinct_values) > 1

 )
 select * from validation_errors
 {% else %}
 validation_errors as (

    select
        count(1) as set_count,
        count(distinct lower(distinct_values)) as set_count_case_insensitive
    from
        test_data

 )
 select *
 from
    validation_errors
 where
    set_count != set_count_case_insensitive
 {% endif %}
 {%- endtest -%}

macro.dbt_expectations.test_expect_colum.macro_sql:
{% test expect_column_values_to_be_within_n_moving_stdevs(model,
                                  column_name,
                                  date_column_name,
                                  group_by=None,
                                  period='day',
                                  lookback_periods=1,
                                  trend_periods=7,
                                  test_periods=14,
                                  sigma_threshold=3,
                                  sigma_threshold_upper=None,
                                  sigma_threshold_lower=None,
                                  take_diffs=true,
                                  take_logs=true
                                ) -%}
    {{ adapter.dispatch('test_expect_column_values_to_be_within_n_moving_stdevs', 'dbt_expectations') (model,
                                  column_name,
                                  date_column_name,
                                  group_by,
                                  period,
                                  lookback_periods,
                                  trend_periods,
                                  test_periods,
                                  sigma_threshold,
                                  sigma_threshold_upper,
                                  sigma_threshold_lower,
                                  take_diffs,
                                  take_logs
                                ) }}
{%- endtest %}

macro.dbt_expectations.default__test_exp.name: default__test_expect_column_values_to_be_within_n_moving_stdevs
macro.dbt_expectations.default__test_exp.macro_sql:
{% macro default__test_expect_column_values_to_be_within_n_moving_stdevs(model,
                                  column_name,
                                  date_column_name,
                                  group_by,
                                  period,
                                  lookback_periods,
                                  trend_periods,
                                  test_periods,
                                  sigma_threshold,
                                  sigma_threshold_upper,
                                  sigma_threshold_lower,
                                  take_diffs,
                                  take_logs
                                ) %}

{%- set sigma_threshold_upper = sigma_threshold_upper if sigma_threshold_upper else sigma_threshold -%}
{%- set sigma_threshold_lower = sigma_threshold_lower if sigma_threshold_lower else -1 * sigma_threshold -%}
{%- set partition_by = "partition by " ~ (group_by | join(",")) if group_by -%}
{%- set group_by_length = (group_by | length ) if group_by else 0 -%}

with metric_values as (

    with grouped_metric_values as (

        select
            {{ dbt.date_trunc(period, date_column_name) }} as metric_period,
            {{ group_by | join(",") ~ "," if group_by }}
            sum({{ column_name }}) as agg_metric_value
        from
            {{ model }}
        {{  dbt_expectations.group_by(1 + group_by_length) }}

    )
    {%- if take_diffs %}
    , grouped_metric_values_with_priors as (

        select
            *,
            lag(agg_metric_value, {{ lookback_periods }}) over(
                {{ partition_by }}
                order by metric_period) as prior_agg_metric_value
    from
        grouped_metric_values d

    )
    select
        *,
        {{ dbt_expectations._get_metric_expression("agg_metric_value", take_logs) }}
        -
        {{ dbt_expectations._get_metric_expression("prior_agg_metric_value", take_logs) }}
        as metric_test_value
    from
        grouped_metric_values_with_priors d

    {%- else %}

    select
        *,
        {{ dbt_expectations._get_metric_expression("agg_metric_value", take_logs) }}
        as metric_test_value
    from
        grouped_metric_values

    {%- endif %}

),
metric_moving_calcs as (

    select
        *,
        avg(metric_test_value)
            over({{ partition_by }}
                    order by metric_period rows
                    between {{ trend_periods }} preceding and 1 preceding) as metric_test_rolling_average,
        stddev(metric_test_value)
            over({{ partition_by }}
                    order by metric_period rows
                    between {{ trend_periods }} preceding and 1 preceding) as metric_test_rolling_stddev
    from
        metric_values

),
metric_sigma as (

    select
        *,
        (metric_test_value - metric_test_rolling_average) as metric_test_delta,
        (metric_test_value - metric_test_rolling_average)/
            nullif(metric_test_rolling_stddev, 0) as metric_test_sigma
    from
        metric_moving_calcs

)
select
    *
from
    metric_sigma
where

    metric_period >= cast(
            {{ dbt.dateadd(period, -test_periods, dbt.date_trunc(period, dbt_date.now())) }}
            as {{ dbt_expectations.type_timestamp() }})
    and
    metric_period < {{ dbt.date_trunc(period, dbt_date.now()) }}
    and

    not (
        metric_test_sigma >= {{ sigma_threshold_lower }} and
        metric_test_sigma <= {{ sigma_threshold_upper }}
    )
{%- endmacro -%}

doc.dbt.__overview__.block_contents:
### Welcome!

Welcome to the auto-generated documentation for your dbt project!

### Navigation

You can use the `Project` and `Database` navigation tabs on the left side of the window to explore the models
in your project.

#### Project Tab
The `Project` tab mirrors the directory structure of your dbt project. In this tab, you can see all of the
models defined in your dbt project, as well as models imported from dbt packages.

#### Database Tab
The `Database` tab also exposes your models, but in a format that looks more like a database explorer. This view
shows relations (tables and views) grouped into database schemas. Note that ephemeral models are _not_ shown
in this interface, as they do not exist in the database.

### Graph Exploration
You can click the blue icon on the bottom-right corner of the page to view the lineage graph of your models.

On model pages, you'll see the immediate parents and children of the model you're exploring. By clicking the `Expand`
button at the top-right of this lineage pane, you'll be able to see all of the models that are used to build,
or are built from, the model you're exploring.

Once expanded, you'll be able to use the `--select` and `--exclude` model selection syntax to filter the
models in the graph. For more information on model selection, check out the [dbt docs](https://docs.getdbt.com/docs/model-selection-syntax).

Note that you can also right-click on models to interactively filter and explore the graph.

---

### More information

- [What is dbt](https://docs.getdbt.com/docs/introduction)?
- Read the [dbt viewpoint](https://docs.getdbt.com/docs/viewpoint)
- [Installation](https://docs.getdbt.com/docs/installation)
- Join the [dbt Community](https://www.getdbt.com/community/) for questions and discussion
